#: of numpy.polynomial.chebyshev.chebinterpolate:12
msgid ""
"The function to be approximated. It must be a function of a single variable "
"of the form ``f(x, a, b, c...)``, where ``a, b, c...`` are extra arguments "
"passed in the `args` parameter."
msgstr ""

